longBusinessSummary: Fourth Wave Energy, Inc. designs energy system to reduce energy consumption and associated carbon emissions in residences and commercial buildings. Its energy system is based on combining solar power and other energy technologies into one fully integrated system. The company is headquartered in San Jose, California.
